Question 13
Consider the following snippet, comment your views.
$sub = substr(12345, 2, 2);
echo “sub is $sub”;

ANSWER
<?php
$number = 9876;
$sum = 0;
$temp = $number;
while ($number > 0) {
    $digit = $number % 10;  
    $sum += $digit;            
    $number = (int)($number / 10); 
}
echo "Sum of digits of $temp is: $sum";
?>


OUTPUT:
Sum of digits of 9876 is: 30

